Package ch.colabproject.colab.api.model.document

Class ResourceRef

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.colabproject.colab.api.model.document.AbstractResource
      • ch.colabproject.colab.api.model.document.ResourceRef
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ColabEntity, WithId, WithJsonDiscriminator, Serializable
    @Entity
public class ResourceRef
extends AbstractResource
    A reference to another existing abstract resource.

    There can be a chain of references to aim at a resource.

    Ref - [Ref -](0..*) Resource

    The resource reference holds the comments for the resource in the context of a specific card / card type / card type reference / card content.

    Author:
    sandra
